WaitTimes.WaitTimeNotes: Vehicle reservations to the San Juan Islands are available at www.takeaferry.com or by calling 511, and must be made at least 2 hours prior to sailing time. Walk-on passengers should arrive at least 15 minutes prior to departure sailing.
